00:10:41.359 --> 00:10:45.479
strive together with me in your prayers to God for me.

00:10:45.479 --> 00:10:49.399
The reality is that the group that's going to Idaho,

00:10:49.399 --> 00:10:52.319
we also need to be engaged in prayer.

00:10:53.999 --> 00:10:55.999
And then we're putting our feet to the ground

00:10:55.999 --> 00:10:56.879
and we're going out

00:10:56.919 --> 00:11:00.159
and actually doing the work of the ministry.

00:11:00.159 --> 00:11:03.599
And he says that you strive together with me

00:11:03.599 --> 00:11:05.839
